<BaseLayout
  title="Ndarakwai Ranch Day Trip | Go Kilimanjaro Treks"
  description="A walking safari on the private 11,000-acre Ndarakwai conservation ranch on the western slopes of Kilimanjaro, supporting Maasai community conservation."
  ogImage="https://gokilimanjarotreks.com/images/daytrip-ndarakwai.jpg"
  ogImageAlt="Plains zebras on Tanzanian savanna at sunrise"
  schemas={schemas}
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <img src="/images/daytrip-ndarakwai.jpg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center 40%;z-index:0;opacity:0.55" />
  <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(100deg,rgba(2,6,14,0.88) 0%,rgba(2,6,14,0.82) 40%,rgba(2,6,14,0.55) 65%,rgba(2,6,14,0.15) 100%);z-index:1"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <span class="page-hero-eyebrow">Tanzania Day Trip</span>
    <h1>Ndarakwai Ranch</h1>
    <p>Explore a pioneering model for community-based conservation on the western slopes of Mount Kilimanjaro. Ndarakwai Ranch is a privately owned, 11,000-acre ranch dedicated to restoring self-sustaining habitats that had been degraded by overgrazing. It offers a unique, intimate wilderness experience where you can see wildlife recovery firsthand.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500" class="btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Nelson</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
    <p style="font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--amber-cta);font-weight:700;margin:30px 0 18px">From $191 per person</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Highlights</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left:22px;margin-bottom:8px">
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Explore an exclusive, private conservation area far away from heavy safari traffic.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Enjoy guided walking safaris to get close to wildlife on foot safely.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Support an eco-friendly project that directly benefits local Maasai communities.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">A Day on This Trip</h2>
    <ol style="padding-left:22px;margin-bottom:8px">
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">07:30 AM: Depart your hotel and head towards the western Kilimanjaro plains.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">09:30 AM: Meet your resident naturalist and head out on an informative walking safari to spot zebras, elands, giraffes, and wildebeests.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">12:30 PM: Enjoy a fresh, locally sourced hot meal at the Ndarakwai tented camp dining room.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">02:00 PM: Take a short drive to see more remote corners of the ranch or learn about local community anti-poaching initiatives.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">04:00 PM: Head back to Arusha, enjoying views of the plains at dusk.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">What is Included</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Private transport, Ndarakwai Ranch conservation fees, services of an experienced resident naturalist, hot lunch, and drinking water.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">What is Not Included</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Alcoholic drinks, tips for ranch staff, and items of a personal nature.</p>
    <p style="font-size:.92rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-top:18px">Every day trip is private and fully customisable. Prices vary with group size and season, so message Nelson for an exact quote for your dates.</p>
  </div>
</section>

