    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:22px">Pair this with another single-day adventure from Moshi or Arusha.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;justify-content:center">
<a href="/daytrips/tarangire" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Tarangire Safari Tour</a>
<a href="/daytrips/materuni-waterfall-coffee" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Materuni Waterfall and Coffee Farm Tour</a>
<a href="/daytrips/arusha-national-park" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Arusha Safari</a>
<a href="/daytrips/ol-doinyo-lengai" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Ol Doinyo Lengai</a>
<a href="/daytrips/kilimanjaro-helicopter-tour" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Kilimanjaro Helicopter Tour</a>
<a href="/daytrips/lake-chala" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Lake Chala</a>
<a href="/daytrips/chemka-hot-springs" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Chemka Hot Springs</a>
<a href="/daytrips/kilimanjaro-day-hike" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Mount Kilimanjaro Day Hikes</a>
<a href="/daytrips/horseback-riding" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Horseback Riding</a>
<a href="/daytrips/arusha-shopping-tour" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Arusha Shopping Tour</a>
<a href="/daytrips/ngorongoro" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--ink-2);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Ngorongoro Crater Day Trip</a>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:24px"><a href="/daytrips" style="color:var(--amber-cta);font-weight:600">See all day trips &#x2192;</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready to <em>Book This Day Trip</em>?</h2>
    <p>Talk to Nelson about your dates and the rest of your time in Tanzania. He responds personally within 24 hours.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="font-size:1.05rem;padding:18px 40px">Request a Quote &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500" class="btn-wa" style="font-size:1rem" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

